A breath-taking landmark and the star of King Kong, An Affair to Remember, and Sleepless in Seattle, the sale has 'sex appeal', realtor Joel Beam told Wall Street Journal.

However, experts warn the building's highlight - the observatory deck - could be cast into shadow by the 104-storey One World Trade Center, set to emerge next door in 2015.

